  <sect1>
    <title>hello.c</title>

<para>下面的例子测试直接在 docbook 文档中写源代码对行号的影响。</para>

<programlisting linenumbering="numbered" startinglinenumber="1" language="c"><?dbhtml linenumbering.everyNth="1" linenumbering.separator=" " linenumbering.width="4"?><?dbfo linenumbering.everyNth="1" linenumbering.separator=" " linenumbering.width="4"?>
<![CDATA[
#include <stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
    printf("hello, world\n");
}
]]>
</programlisting>

  </sect1>

